tags.name: magazine-cover
tags.description:
`magazine-cover`
`A Magazine cover element`
  Example:
  ```html
  <magazine-cover image="demo/picture2.jpg" header="Sunset" action="Click, Breath, Relax" link="https://www.elmsln.org/">
    A simple time, a simple life. America may be fast paced and brutal on health but in Canada, people enjoy sitting and watching the sunset. Learn how Canadians manage stress.
  </magazine-cover>
  ```

Attributes:

  * `header` {`string`} - Title / heading

  * `subheader` {`string`} - A secondary title

  * `text` {`string`} - Internal text.

  * `image` {`string`} - Title / heading

  * `action` {`string`} - Call to action

  * `icon` {`string`} - Call to action icon

  * `link` {`string`} - Link to go to on click.

  * `event-name` {`string`} - Optional event binding for the button press.

  * `event-data` - Optional event data to send along

Properties:

  * `header` {`string`} - Title / heading

  * `subheader` {`string`} - A secondary title

  * `text` {`string`} - Internal text.

  * `image` {`string`} - Title / heading

  * `action` {`string`} - Call to action

  * `icon` {`string`} - Call to action icon

  * `link` {`string`} - Link to go to on click.

  * `eventName` {`string`} - Optional event binding for the button press.

  * `eventData` - Optional event data to send along
